    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for even the most discerning buyer. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior paint and pristine bodywork to the factory-fresh interior that still retains its original luster. Mechanically, it is in perfect working order, having been maintained to the highest standards with no signs of wear or aging. Buyers can expect a showroom-quality vehicle that drives as well as it looks, offering a premium experience without compromise.",
