      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s super comfortable, drives like a dream, and has plenty of life left in it for your next adventure. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I think you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through a true 6-speed manual transmission. Engineered for the purist, it boasts individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut thanks to a limited-slip variable M differential and recent trailing arm bushing replacements. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system overhaul and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. While the finish shows minor road patina, the powertrain remains robust, offering linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response.",
